    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a reliable daily driver that has seen its fair share of the road. The exterior has some noticeable paint chips and a few minor door dings, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs fine, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle for someone looking for affordable transportation, but please expect the cosmetic and mechanical character of a car that has been well-used.",
