    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained vehicle. This model has undergone a rigorous multi-point professional inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for safety and road-readiness. Featuring a clean interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a refined driving experience that rivals newer models. This is a premier opportunity to own a well-cared-for vehicle that delivers both prestige and long-term value. Secure this exceptional find today.",
      "price": 34900.0,
