    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for weekend cruises and has never missed a beat. It\u2019s got that classic soul you just don\u2019t find in modern cars, and honestly, every time I get behind the wheel, I can't help but smile. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and ready for its next adventure\u2014it\u2019s got just a tiny bit of honest character from the road, but that just shows it\u2019s been loved and enjoyed properly! Come on by, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself how she purrs.",
